name: ONIMATA - VOL.03
description:
VOL.03 "TEIKO IS HERE!"

O-01 is awake! O-03 has successfully make him realise that the void was just an illusion made by the TEIKO. It looks like they were trapped in the middle of the fight. This is going to be a mess because seeing TEIKO means something could go BAD in the end.

TEIKO is a group of ONIMATA where all the crew believes that their duty is to protect the weak, to revolt and never obey the current made up law. But sometimes they took the wrong way to do what they believe is right.

Are they going to survive?
